开支持哈里斯，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-endorses-kamala-harris-at-houston-rally-im-here-as-a-mother-3806513">碧昂丝</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-john-legend-and-more-endorse-kamala-harris-for-us-president-3776745">查莉·XCX</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-shares-endorsement-for-kamala-harris-3808708">麦当娜</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-stars-in-hopes-and-dreams-campaign-ad-for-kamala-harris-3809008">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-megan-thee-stallion-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-3779500">梅根·泰·斯塔林、夸沃</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprio-and-bad-bunny-have-endorsed-kamala-harris-3806836">坏兔子</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/st-vincent-endorses-kamala-harris-says-her-grandmother-wouldnt-have-stood-for-disrespect-from-trump-3808930">圣文森特</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-endorses-kamala-harris-at-wisconsin-rally-she-shows-empathy-and-most-of-all-she-is-not-delusional-3808932">卡迪·B</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-mumford-sons-push-for-voting-plan-as-they-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-3808418">芒福德父子公司</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-days-billie-joe-armstrong-urges-fans-to-vote-for-kamala-harris-trump-has-got-to-go-3809609">绿日乐队的比利·乔阿姆斯特朗</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evanescences-amy-lee-proudly-support-kamala-harris-us-presidential-election-3808586">伊凡塞斯的艾米·李</a>。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-days-billie-joe-armstrong-urges-fans-to-vote-for-kamala-harris-trump-has-got-to-go-3809609"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/kamala-harris-makes-surprise-snl-appe